item.title: Tokkul-scape 508 how to make myself owner
item.dc:creator: @tb1 tb
item.description:
@tb1 wrote:

508 mainly has only three.

0 = non staff member
1 = moderator
2 = administrator

but on rare occations:
3 = owner/co-owner (this is only in SOME 508 SERVERS, MOST OF THEM ONLY HAVE 0-2)
